						<summary>

						<p>This is an incomplete inscription stopping with the mention of the boundaries. It records a gift of 4 <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> of land tax-free near the channel of Śivallavaṉ-pēraṇai (dam) (by order of the king ?) to one Eṉṉaiāḷa-uḍaiyār, a disciple of Aghōradēvar of the Āmuṇḍar-maḍam and Śrī Nandikēśvara-santāna.</p>						

						</summary>
